! This is work in progress.

 * "make" uses "uglifyjs" for compressing the *.js files.
 * To create a working TW you need to install "cook". "ginsu" is optional.

 * ViewMode uses syntaxhighlighting allready
    * `{{{` .. plain text
    * `//{{{` .. code
    * `/*{{{*/` .. css
    * `<!--{{{-->` .. xml
    
    
